```

The chart's headless Service is named `<release>-git-server-experimental-headless` (suffix `-headless`), and the StatefulSet itself is `<release>-git-server-experimental` (no suffix). The pod DNS shape is `<sts-name>-N.<headless-svc-name>.<ns>.svc.cluster.local`. So the existing Phase 1 `shardUrl` correctly:
- Takes the headless service name (with `-headless` suffix).
- Strips `-headless` to derive the STS name (which is the pod hostname prefix).
- Renders the pod's stable DNS.

