// ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
// Client-side shard URL composer.
//
// Production hot path: given a workspaceId, return the URL of the storage-
// tier shard that owns it. Composes the Phase 1 primitives:
//
//   - shardForWorkspace(wsId, shards) → index
